(589, 101, 'frm_dyncontent', '<p>Travel Request Title:  <strong>[167]</strong><br>\r\nTravel Requestor: <strong>[83]</strong>  <br>In accordance with approvals from Government POC: <u>[85]</u> and Project Lead: <u>[116 show=357]</u> on delivery order <strong>[116 show=109]</strong> and the <strong>[116]</strong> project.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Traveling from <u>[120], [123]</u> on <u>[122]</u> to <u>[127], [129]</u> on <u>[126]</u>.  <br>A total of <u>[131]</u> days and <u>[132]</u> nights is being requested.</p>\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<p>This request is justified by the following statement and corresponding attachment from the requestor.<p/>\r\n<p><strong><em>[130]</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\nAttachments:  [95]\r\n<hr>\r\n<h4>Estimated Costs for the Trip</h4>\r\n<table class="trav_cost_tbl">\r\n  <tr class="trav_tr_header">\r\n    <th>Description</th>\r\n    <th>Cost</th>\r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td>Per Diem Lodging Rate</td>\r\n    <td class="trav_td_right">[149]</td>   \r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td>Per Diem Meals and Incidentals Expense Rate</td>\r\n    <td class="trav_td_right">[150]</td>   \r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td class="trav_td_right"><strong>Total Allowance</strong></td>\r\n    <td class="trav_td_right"><strong>[151]</strong></td>   \r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td></td>\r\n    <td></td>   \r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td>Airline Cost<sup>1</sup></td>\r\n    <td class="trav_td_right">[138]</td>   \r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td>Airline Fees</td>\r\n    <td class="trav_td_right">[147]</td>   \r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td class="trav_td_right"><strong>Total Airline Cost</strong></td>\r\n    <td class="trav_td_right"><strong>[148]</strong></td>   \r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td></td>\r\n    <td></td>   \r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td>Car Rental Cost</td>\r\n    <td class="trav_td_right">[140]</td>   \r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td>Fuel Cost</td>\r\n    <td class="trav_td_right">[141]</td>   \r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td class="trav_td_right"><strong>Total Rental Cost</strong></td>\r\n    <td class="trav_td_right"><strong>[146]</strong></td>   \r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td></td>\r\n    <td></td>   \r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td >Lodging Cost Per Night</td>\r\n    <td class="trav_td_right">[143]</td>   \r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td>Lodging Tax per Night</td>\r\n    <td class="trav_td_right">[144]</td>   \r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td class="trav_td_right"><strong>Total Lodging Cost</strong></td>\r\n    <td class="trav_td_right"><strong>[145]</strong></td>   \r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td></td>\r\n    <td></td>   \r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td>POV Cost per Mile</td>\r\n    <td class="trav_td_right">[153]</td>   \r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td>Total POV mileage</td>\r\n    <td class="trav_td_right">[154]</td>   \r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td class="trav_td_right"><strong>Total Privately Owned Vehicle Cost</strong></td>\r\n    <td class="trav_td_right"><strong>[155]</strong></td>   \r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td></td>\r\n    <td></td>   \r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td>Limo / Taxi</td>\r\n    <td class="trav_td_right">[157]</td>   \r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td>Parking</td>\r\n    <td class="trav_td_right">[158]</td>   \r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td>Tolls</td>\r\n    <td class="trav_td_right">[159]</td>   \r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td>Other<sup>2</sup></td>\r\n    <td class="trav_td_right">[160]</td>   \r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td class="trav_td_right"><strong>Total Other Expenses</strong></td>\r\n    <td class="trav_td_right"><strong>[163]</strong></td>   \r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td><hr></td>\r\n    <td><hr></td>   \r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td class="trav_td_right"><strong>Grand Total</strong></td>\r\n    <td class="trav_td_right"><strong>[162]</strong></td>   \r\n  </tr>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<p><sub>1 - If Air Travel was selected then the following Airport Codes were provided by the requestor: from <em>[136]</em> to <em>[137]</em></sub></p>\r\n<p><sub>2 - If an amount 