(180, 1, '2014-06-26 22:19:30', '2014-06-26 22:19:30', 'All personnel must submit all travel requests prior to their travel date. All travel must be within Government per diem or have written justification that will be provided with invoice. Itemized travel expense reports are required with all travel costs invoiced.\n\n<hr />\n\n<ol>\n	<li><strong>CONUS Travel</strong> should be requested <strong><em>two weeks</em></strong> prior to travel</li>\n	<li><strong>OCONUS Travel</strong> should be requested <em><strong>one month</strong></em> prior to travel</li>\n</ol>\n\n<hr />\n\n<blockquote>If a travel request is submitted after the request window indicated above then the justification area of the form must include all of the following:</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<ul>\n	<li>why the request was not submitted within the travel request time period</li>\n	<li>why the travel is required</li>\n	<li>what impacts to the project will occur if the travel does not happen at the indicated time</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '5-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-06-26 22:19:30', '2014-06-26 22:19:30', '', 5, 'http://dev.webtravelportal.net/?p=180', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
